This program allows you to track the progress of students who are signed to four different courses.
- enter 'add students' to append a new student to a database
- enter 'add points' to increase a score of student in his exams
- enter 'list' to show list of current students in database by their id
- enter 'find' to check student's score 
- enter 'statistics' to view information about popularity of courses
- enter 'notify' to send email for students that managed to finish a course.
